all right...

asked me to...say hi... So...$k$pBye now!

ya'll—uh, you all... So... I'm pleased
to be here.

Excuse me, $Nu...$k$pA-actually, never mind...$k$pBut, actually... Um, well...$k$pMaybe you already know this about
me, but I'm just a country gal...$k$pI don't take to talkin' all that often on

embarrassing...$k$pBut I just wanted to tell ya... Well...$k$pThanks.
You wanna talk ta me? Ugh, I mean...talk with me?
We aren't really much with fancy talk. I'm just...trying to speak like you.
Yeesh... Can't make out halfa what these castle-breds say.
You heard the way I talk, but that's just the way I talk.
You shouldn't work y'self to death. Good ta no one then!
